member.summary:
protected internal virtual GisSharpBlog.NetTopologySuite.Geometries.Envelope NTSEnvelope
{
   get
   {
       //return this.m_NTSEnvelope;
       return new GisSharpBlog.NetTopologySuite.Geometries.Envelope(
                       this.Envelope.UpperLeft.X, this.Envelope.LowerRight.X, 
                       this.Envelope.UpperLeft.Y, this.Envelope.LowerRight.Y);

member.example:

아래 예제들은 각 함수들의 사용 방법과 반환 결과를 보여준다.

1. Create, Start, Stop, AddText, DeleteText, UpdateText 함수의 사용 예

            using System;
            ...
            class Program
            {
                static void Main(string[] args)
                {
                    // Splash Windows 설정
                    Font _font = new Font("맑은고딕", 30, FontStyle.Bold); 
                    Brush _brush = new SolidBrush(Color.Red); ; 
                    int _iSizeX = 700; 
                    int _iSizeY = 350; 
                    int _iSwitchInterval = 1000; 
                    double dOpacity = 50;

                    // Splash Windows 생성
                    SplashWindows.Create(_strImageFilePathList, _font, _brush, dOpacity, _iSizeX, _iSizeY, _iSwitchInterval);
                    Console.WriteLine("Splash Windows 생성.");        

                    // Splash Windows 시작
                    SplashWindows.Start();
                    Console.WriteLine("Splash Windows 시작.");

                    // Splash Windows 중지
                    SplashWindows.Stop();
                    Console.WriteLine("Splash Windows 중지.");

                    // Add Text 설정
                    string _strStatusMessage = "Test";
                    int _iX = 100; 
                    int _iY = 100;
                    int _iID = 0;

                    // Add Text 실행
                    SplashWindows.AddText(_iID, _strStatusMessage, _iX, _iY);
                    Console.WriteLine(string.Format("Add Text Message : {0}", _strStatusMessage));

                    // Update Text 실행
                    string _strNewStatusMessage = "Update Test";
                    SplashWindows.UpdateText(_iID, _strNewStatusMessage);
                    Console.WriteLine(string.Format("Update Text Message : {0}", _strNewStatusMessage));

                    // Delete Text 실행
                    SplashWindows.DeleteText(_iID);
                    Console.WriteLine("Delete Text Message");
                }
            }


[결과]

            Splash Windows 생성.
            Splash Windows 시작.
            Splash Windows 중지.
            Add Text Message : Test
            Update Text Message : Update Test
            Delete Text Message

